  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Peel and finely dice the <strong>shallots</strong></p><p>Mash the <strong>beluga lentils</strong> in a large bowl to form a rough paste</p><p>Add the<strong> diced shallots</strong>, <strong>ground allspice</strong>, <strong>ground</strong> <strong>cinnamon</strong>, and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Season with a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and mix thoroughly to combine (clean hands is the best way!)</p>",
